be%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20in%20UAE%20and%20Pakistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib%2C%20who%20was%20named%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20after%20the%20anti-discrimination%20protests%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20raised%20concerns%20over%20his%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20great%2C%20who%20featured%20in%20129%20T20Is%20for%20Bangladesh%20will%2C%20however%2C%20continue%20to%20play%20in%20franchise%20leagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20played%20my%20last%20T20%20match%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20We%20have%20discussed%20this%20with%20the%20selectors.%20Looking%20at%20the%202026%20World%20Cup%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20time%20for%20me%20to%20move%20out.%20Hopefully%2C%20BCB%20will%20find%20some%20great%20players%20and%20we%20will%20perform%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shakib%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20second%20and%20final%20Test%20against%20India%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib%2C%20who%20has%20played%2070%20Tests%2C%20scoring%204600%20runs%20and%20taking%20242%20wickets%20might%20just%20play%20his%20last%20Test%20in%20the%20North%20Indian%20industrial%20town%20in%20case%20the%20cricket%20board%20can't%20assure%20him%20of%20his%20security%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20murder%20although%20he%20wasn't%20even%20in%20the%20country%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20available%20for%20the%20South%20Africa%20series%20but%20since%20there's%20a%20lot%20happening%20back%20home%2C%20naturally%20not%20everything%20depends%20on%20me.%20I%20have%20discussed%20my%20plans%20about%20Test%20cricket%20with%20the%20BCB.%20Especially%20this%20series%20and%20the%20home%20series.%20I%20was%20thinking%20that%20it%20could%20be%20my%20last%20Test%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fshakib-al-hasan-says-he-s-done-with-t20is-and-will-play-his-final-test-next-month-1452683%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPN%20Cricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20told%20%5BBCB%20president%5D%20Faruque%20%5BAhmed%5D%20bhai%20and%20the%20selectors.%20If%20there's%20a%20chance%20and%20if%20I%20can%20play%2C%20my%20last%20Test%20will%20be%20in%20Mirpur.%20The%20board%20is%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20I%20can%20play%20and%20feel%20safe%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20I%20can%20leave%20the%20country%20without%20a%20hitch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20citizen%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20so%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20any%20problem%20going%20back%20to%20Bangladesh.%20My%20concern%20is%20my%20safety%20and%20security%20in%20Bangladesh.%20My%20close%20friends%20and%20family%20members%20are%20concerned.%20I%20hope%20things%20are%20getting%20better.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20solution%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib%20was%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20back%20home%20during%20the%20political%20unrest%20that%20led%20to%20the%20ouster%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%20He%20was%20a%20member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20her%20party%2C%20the%20Awami%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20tough%20for%20me.%20Only%20Allah%20knows%20how%20I%20am%20focused%20on%20the%20game.%20Even%20I%20don't%20know.%20There%20is%20a%20case%20against%20me.%20Everyone%20has%20the%20rights.%20You%20all%20know%20what%20type%20of%20case%20it%20is%20or%20where%20I%20was%20and%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20at%20that%20time.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20talk%20much%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20ESPNCricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib%20made%20the%20announcement%20while%20interacting%20with%20Bangladeshi%20media%20but%20spoke%20in%20English%20following%20a%20request%20from%20the%20Indian%20journalists.%20In%20an%20unexpected%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20Shakib%20was%20named%20in%20an%20FIR%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20related%20to%20the%20civil%20protests%20in%20Bangladesh