0The%20most%20recent%20new%20US%20nuclear%20plant%2C%20built%20by%20Georgia%20Power%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fgeorgia-nuclear-power-plant-vogtle-rates-costs-75c7a413cda3935dd551be9115e88a64%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrived%20seven%20years%20late%20and%20%2417%20billion%20over%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20Mile%20Island%20could%20run%20into%20similar%20problems%2C%20said%20Tim%20Judson%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Nuclear%20Information%20and%20Resource%20Service%2C%20which%20advocates%20against%20nuclear%20power%20and%20for%20renewables%20like%20solar%20and%20wind.%20He%20noted%20that%20the%20plant%20needed%20licensing%20approvals%20from%20the%20Nuclear%20Regulatory%20Commission%20and%20that%20reviving%20an%20old%20reactor%20that's%20been%20idle%20for%20five%20years%20could%20prove%20technically%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarr%C3%B3n%20of%20Constellation%20Energy%20acknowledged%20that%20even%20with%20new%20federal%20tax%20breaks%20for%20nuclear%20energy%2C%20Three%20Mile%20Island%20wouldn't%20be%20economical%20to%20run%20without%20the%20deal%20with%20Microsoft.%20Restarting%20the%20plant%20requires%20NRC%20approval%20following%20a%20safety%20and%20environmental%20review%2C%20as%20well%20as%20permits%20from%20state%20and%20local%20agencies.%20Constellation%20Energy%20said%20it%20will%20pursue%20a%20separate%20license%20renewal%20that%20extends%20operations%20to%20at%20least%202054.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudson%20is%20also%20concerned%20that%20Constellation%20Energy%20is%20talking%20to%20a%20regional%20grid%20operator%2C%20PJM%2C%20about%20putting%20the%20nuclear%20plant%20in%20front%20of%20a%20long%20queue%20of%20solar%2C%20wind%2C%20and%20battery%20storage%20projects%20waiting%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20grid.%20He%20argued%20there'd%20be%20no%20need%20for%20a%20nuclear%20revival%20if%20renewable%20projects%20cleared%20those%20roadblocks%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuclear's%20supporters%20disagree%2C%20including%20Arshad%20Mansoor%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Electric%20Power%20Research%20Institute.%20He%20told%20BI%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20renewables%20and%20battery%20storage%20will%20be%20enough%20to%20bring%20the%20economy%20to%20net-zero%20emissions.%20Data%20centers%20aren't%20the%20only%20driver%20of%20power%20demand.%20Electric%20vehicles%20and%20new%20manufacturing%20plants%20need%20electricity%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMansoor%20thinks%20the%20AI%20boom%20will%20actually%20accelerate%20a%20greener%20economy%2C%20noting%20that%20tech%20companies%20sparked%20greater%20deployment%20of%20wind%20and%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20they've%20created%20a%20second%20spark%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20just%20be%20nuclear%2C%26quot%3B%20Mansoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20predicted%20greater%20buy-in%20for%20geothermal%2C%20long-duration%20battery%20storage%2C%20and%20carbon%20capture%20and%20storage%20at%20gas%20plants%20%E2%80%94%20many%20more%20of%20which%20will%20be%20built%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20Mansoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20echoed%20what%20many%20tech%20executives%20said%20when%20defending%20AI's%20energy%20consumption%3A%20It%20will%20reduce%20emissions%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20such%20as%20by%20helping%20utilities%20manage%20the%20grid%20more%20efficiently%20and%20deploy%20renewables%20at%20peak%20demand%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20still%20isn't%20clear%20whether%20such%20benefits%20can%20offset%20soaring%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-bank-of-america-nuclear-power-ai-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727348491000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f4b205de59ade1a3b4abbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-bank-of-america-nuclear-power-ai-2024-9%22%2