ve%20been%20into%20computers%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid.%20When%20I%20started%20my%20career%2C%20there%20were%20no%20university%20degrees%20in%20hacking.%20I%20taught%20myself%20and%20learned%20through%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20in%20cyber%20security%20for%20almost%2010%20years%20now.%20I%20started%20as%20a%20consultant%2C%20doing%20what%20we%20call%20%26quot%3Bpenetration%20testing%26quot%3B%3A%20hacking%20into%20companies'%20websites%2C%20mobile%20apps%2C%20and%20IT%20infrastructure%20to%20fix%20vulnerabilities%20in%20their%20systems.%20I've%20also%20helped%20companies%20to%20recover%20from%20hacking%20incidents%3A%20we%20call%20it%20%26quot%3Bincident%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20head%20of%20threat%20intelligence%20at%20F-Secure%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20company%20in%20Finland%2C%20for%20two%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20analyze%20internet%20attacks%20and%20conduct%20research%20into%20how%20people%20are%20targeted.%20Once%20we%20understand%20how%20a%20scam%20works%2C%20we%20add%20it%20to%20our%20database%20and%20can%20innovate%20new%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20find%20it%20worrying%20how%20technology%20can%20be%20misused%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20kinds%20of%20misuse%20are%20only%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22452b9e49-09b8-4388-82eb-a1125bf414b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECybercrime%20is%20usually%20about%20getting%20money%20out%20of%20the%20victim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECybercrime%20is%20almost%20always%20about%20money.%20Sometimes%2C%20it's%20a%20ransomware%20attack%2C%20where%20malware%20%E2%80%94%20software%20designed%20for%20malicious%20intent%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20a%20system%20inoperable.%20The%20company%20or%20individual%20is%20then%20asked%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20release%20of%20their%20IT%20infrastructure%2C%20data%2C%20or%20whatever%20has%20been%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20gains%20access%20to%20your%20online%20accounts%20or%20gets%20malware%20installed%20on%20your%20devices%2C%20it's%20very%20likely%20that%20the%20stolen%20data%20ends%20up%20being%20for%20sale%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fadvisor%2Fvpn%2Fcybercrime-statistics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybercriminals%20steal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20attempt%20to%20steal%20%E2%80%94%20more%20money%20from%20companies%20and%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20my%20career%2C%20many%20of%20the%20threats%20we%20saw%20were%20somewhat%20abstract%2C%20and%20their%20impact%20wasn't%20as%20widespread.%20I%20remember%20some%20of%20the%20first%20instances%20of%20ransomware%20that%20hit%20Finland.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20these%20attacks%20were%20few%20and%20far%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20course%20of%20my%20career%2C%20technology%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20our%20lives%3A%20we%20carry%20our%20phones%20with%20us%20all%20the%20time%2C%20work%20remotely%2C%20have%20email%20and%20phone%20numbers%2C%20and%20use%20social%20media%2C%20dating%2C%20and%20gaming%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20so%20much%20exposure%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20which%20makes%20us%20easier%20to%20target.%20Our%20data%20is%20becoming%20more%20valuable%2C%20and%20there%20are%20more%20ways%20that%20cybercriminals%20can%20benefit%20from%20stealing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225da0fa55-29cf-469a-bf79-9f2ac3c77c6c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHackers%20can%20access%20more%20information%20than%20you'd%20think%20possible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fareena.yle.fi%2F1-4664681%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinnish%20TV%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20people%20understand%20the%20impact%20of%20hacking%2C%20we%20hacked%20into%20a%20person's%20computer%20with%20her%20permission.%20The%20volunteer%20still%20fell%20for%20our%20scam%2C%20even%20knowing%20she%20would%20be%20hacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20created%20fake%20profiles%20online%2C%20taking%20time%20to%20craft%20them%20so%20they'd%20appear%20as%20real%20people.%20On%20LinkedIn%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20gained%20as%20many%20connections%20as%20possible%20so%20that%20she%20would%20accept%20without%20question%20when%20we%20reached%20out%20to%20our%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we'd%20accomplished%20that%2C%20we%20directed%20her%20to%20a%20phishing%20site%20we%20had%20developed.%20It%20was%20a%20website%20that%20looked%20like%20Google%2C%20which%20we%20used%20to%20steal%20her%20credentials.%20We%20created%20a%20piece%20of%20malware%20that%20we%20convinced%20her%20to%20install%2C%20giving%20us%20full%20access%20to%20her%20PC%20and%20its%20data.%20We%20even%20turned%20on%20her%20webcam%20and%20recorded%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20flashy%20example%20was%20made%20for%20entertainment%2C%20but%20it%20still%20showcased%20how%20real%20criminals%20use%20fake%20profiles%2C%20phishing%20websites%2C%20and%20malware%20to%20compromise%20a%20person%20or%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf3a9d25-5286-44f1-9f78-7f4f606e543c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20scams%20are%20being%20developed%20every%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20see%20multiple%20new%20scams%20or%20cyber%20security%20problems%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20have%20uncovered%20a%20Telegram%20bot%20that%20generates%20and%20shares%20malware%20in%20the%20language%20based%20on%20the%20country%20code%20of%20the%20user's%20phone%20number%3B%20we%20discovered%20a%20scam%20where%20Android%20malware%20was%20disguised%20as%20wedding%20guest%20invitations%3B%20we%20have%20looked%20into%20scammers%20creating%20fake%20profiles%20based%20on%20recently%20deceased%20people%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScams%20and%20the%20whole%20ecosystem%20around%20them%20are%20becoming%20more%20sophisticated%2C%20and%20I%20think%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScammers%20have%20developed%20phishing%20toolkits%20that%20are%20freely%20available%20on%20the%20internet%3A%20step-by-step%20guidance%20on%20how%20to%20set%20up%20phishing%20attacks%20or%20ready-made%20websites%20that%20look%20like%20social%20media%20platforms%20with%20built-in%20phishing%20tools%2C%20so%20scammers%20don't%20need%20to%20know%20how%20to%20write%20code.%20You%20can%20even%20buy%20malware%20online%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20kind%20of%20help%20desk%20for%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECybercrime%20is%20easier%20to%20do%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20and%20these%20toolkits%20will%20become%20more%20advanced%20and%20widely%20available.%20It's%20a%20big%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20increasingly%20being%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20these%20attacks.%20It's%20creating%20better-looking%20scams%2C%20while%20deepfakes%2C%20voice%20clones%2C%20and%20video%20filters%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20fool%20people%20into%20believing%20things%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20seeing%20romance%20scams%20where%20scammers%20are%20using%20deepfake%20video%20filter%20tools%20to%20pretend%20to%20be%20celebrities%2C%20for%20instance.%20They%20find%20people%20on%20dating%20apps%2C%20take%20the%20conversation%20to%20an%20instant%20messaging%20app%20and%20have%20a%20video%20chat%2C%20using%20filters%20to%20mimic%20someone%20else's%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20it%20used%20for%20investment%20scams%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20where%20a%20CEO's%20voice%20has%20been%20cloned%20with%20an%20AI%20tool%20and%20used%20to%20send%20a%20voice%20note%20over%20WhatsApp%20asking%20for%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20cyber%20security%20is%20being%20taken%20more%20seriously%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20banging%20my%20head%20against%20a%20wall%2C%20and%20nothing%20is%20changing.%20But%20I%20do%20think%20that%20my%20work%20is%20doing%20something%20good%20every%20day%20and%20helping%20people.%20I'm%20hoping%20to%20do%20more%20of%20that%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhacker-online-scams-getting-worse-ai-cybersecurity-expert-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727347752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f441fb0d59cc64f5b02312%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhacker-online-scams-getting-worse-ai-cybersecurity-expert-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Laura%20Kankaala%2C%20whose%20worked%20in%20cybersecurity%20for%2010%20years%2C%20said%20that%20online%20scams%20are%20becoming%20more%20complex%20and%20easier%20for%20criminals%20to%20execute.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Emma%20Magnus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhacker-online-scams-getting-worse-ai-cybersecurity-expert-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20upstart%20planemaker%20is%20taking%20advantage%20of%20production%20woes%20at%20Boeing%20and%20Airbus%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20break%20into%20the%20Western%20market%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223150%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China's%20self-developed%20passenger%20jet%20C919%20makes%20its%20first%20international%20debut%20in%20a%20flight%20demonstration%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Airshow%20on%20February%2020%2C%202024%20in%20Singapore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66507c2e20abc1efe8fd43f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20C919%2C%20Chinese%20planemaker%20Comac's%20competitor%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20Airbus%20A320%20and%20Boeing%20737.%3Cp%3EWan%20Quan%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBrazil's%20Total%20Linhas%20Aereas%20is%20in%20talks%20to%20buy%20up%20to%20four%20Comac%20C919%20jets%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3