r%20gift%20shop%20and%20another%20Grand%20Teton%20National%20Park%20store%20selling%20various%20goods%2C%20from%20clothing%20to%20water%20bottles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20about%20how%20Grand%20Teton%20visitors%20could%20spend%20more%20time%20exploring%20the%20park%20and%20save%20the%20shopping%20for%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20thoughtfully%20organized%20trash%20station%20was%20a%20welcome%20surprise.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20an%20airport%20terminal%20with%20wood%20ceilings%20and%20a%20trash%20organizing%20facility%20in%20the%20foreground%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2d3f0cfb7f307e5745173%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaste%20receptacles%20in%20the%20terminal.%20%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20airports%2C%20and%20I%20rarely%20see%20trash%20that's%20this%20organized.%20The%20categories%20even%20separated%20magazines%20from%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20the%20gate%2C%20I%20spotted%20updated%20charging%20ports%20beneath%20the%20chairs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20stellar%20view.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Seats%20in%20an%20airport%20terminal%20with%20windows%20behind%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f44d44de59ade1a3b490f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20gate%20inside%20the%20terminal.%20%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20waiting%20for%20flights%20at%20JAC%20don't%20need%20a%20screen.%20The%20views%20out%20the%20wide%20windows%20lining%20the%20terminal%20are%20entertainment%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20was%20grateful%20to%20be%20able%20to%20charge%20my%20devices.%20Each%20power%20strip%20beneath%20nearly%20every%20seat%