6quot%3BFalse%20Records%20Created%20In%20Police%20Station%26quot%3B%3A%20Agency's%20Big%20Claim%20In%20RG%20Kar%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frg-kar-rape-murder-case%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERG%20Kar%20Hospital%20rape-murder%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20told%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Kolkata%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20false%20records%2C%20pertaining%20to%20the%20case%2C%20were%20created%20at%20the%20Tala%20Police%20Station%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20agency%2C%20tasked%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20with%20investigating%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20junior%20doctor%20last%20month%2C%20also%20said%20it%20had%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20police%20station%20in%20question%2C%20and%20that%20this%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20a%20central%20forensics%20lab%20in%20the%20city%20for%20examination.%20Kolkata%20Police%20has%20not%20yet%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20significant%20twist%20in%20the%20case%20comes%20after%20the%20CBI%20interrogated%20Abhijit%20Mondal%2C%20the%20officer-in-charge%20of%20the%20Tala%20Police%20Station%20at%20the%20time.%20Mondal%2C%C2%A0arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20tampering%20with%20evidence%2C%20and%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20hospital's%20former%20chief%2C%20held%20over%20financial%20irregularities%2C%20are%20both%20in%20CBI%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20suspect%20Sanjay%20Roy%20-%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20with%20the%20cops%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20on%20CCTV%20footage%20entering%20the%20room%20in%20which%20the%20body%20was%20found%2C%20hours%20before%20it%20was%20-%20has%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20the%20agency%20had%20produced%20Mondal%20and%20Ghosh%20before%20the%20court%20following%20completion%20of%20their%20remand.%20The%20court%20subsequently%20sent%20them%20to%20judicial%20custody%20till%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20agency%20told%20the%20court%20it%20suspects%20a%20'nexus'%20between%20the%20two%3B%20the%20CBI%20referred%20to%20phone%20calls%20between%20Mondal%20and%20Ghosh.%20Mondal's%20lawyer%20pointed%20out%20that%20given%20a%20serious%20crime%20had%20been%20reported%20from%20the%20hospital%20it%20was%20normal%20for%20the%20two%20to%20speak%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20point%20was%20flagged%20in%20the%20trial%20court%20yet%20again%20today%2C%20and%20the%20defence%20pointed%20out%20the%20CBI%2C%20though%20it%20had%20made%20these%20critical%20allegations%2C%20had%20not%20provided%20evidence%20to%20back%20its%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20identifying%20those%20guilty%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20junior%20doctor%2C%20the%20CBI%20is%20also%20investigating%20reports%20of%20destruction%20of%20evidence%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20rape%20and%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondal%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20said%2C%20is%20not%20accused%20in%20the%20rape%20or%20murder%2C%20but%20may%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20cover-up%20that%20followed.%20The%20Bengal%20government%20and%20police%20force%20are%20facing%20severe%20scrutiny%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20with%20many%20alleging%20the%20state%20is%20trying%20to%20protect%20those%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20also%20probing%20a%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20between%20Mondal%2C%20Ghosh%2C%20and%20Roy%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20delay%20of%20two%20days%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20seizure%20of%20the%20clothes%20the%20latter%20wore%20on%20the%20day.%20This%2C%20the%20agency%20told%20the%20court%2C%20could%20have%20led%20to%20contamination%20of%20material%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20points%20of%20order%20flagged%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20(which%20took%20suo%20moto%20cognisance)%20is%20that%20there%20was%20a%2014-hour%20delay%20between%20finding%20the%20body%20and%20filing%20a%20police%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20courts%20have%20demanded%20to%20know%20why%20the%20hospital%20administration%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20did%20not%20do%20so%20immediately%2C%20which%20would%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20have%20ensured%20the%20police%20filed%20a%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20aside%2C%20Mondal%20was%20last%20night%20admitted%20to%20the%20prison%20hospital.%20Sources%20told%20news%20agency%20IANS%20he%20tripped%20and%20fell%20while%20being%20taken%20back%20from%20the%20court%20after%20yesterday's%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20on%20Sunday%20the%20CBI%20also%20questioned%20another%20doctor%20-%20Birupaksha%20Biswas%2C%20allegedly%20close%20to%20Ghosh%20-%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20rape%20and%20murder.%20Biswas%20was%20reportedly%20part%20of%20the%20'North%20Bengal%20lobby'%2C%20which%20medics%20in%20the%20state%20say%20have%20threatened%20medical%20students%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20junior%20doctors%20partially%20rejoined%20duties%20after%20striking%20for%20over%2040%20days%20to%20protest%20the%20killing%20of%20their%20colleague.%20They%20rejoined%20for%20essential%20and%20emergency%20services%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20been%20protesting%20since%20August%209%20-%20which%20has%20included%20three%20failed%20attempts%20at%20talks%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20-%20for%20justice%20for%20their%20colleague%20and%20removal%20of%20three%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20Health%20Secretary%2C%20alleging%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20made%20it%20clear%20this%20partial%20return%20is%20not%20an%20end%20to%20their%20agitation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20needed%2C%20we%20will%20begin%20protests%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727345520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%