lity%20to%20somewhat%20surreptitiously%20record%20video.%20Now%2C%20despite%20a%20rocky%20start%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20Meta's%20smart%20glasses%20are%20doing%20better%20than%20expected.%20That's%20a%20low%20bar%2C%20given%20how%20deeply%20its%20first%20generation%20of%20the%20Ray-Ban%20glasses%20from%202021%20disappointed%20%E2%80%94%20selling%20only%20about%20300%2C000%20pairs%2C%20less%20than%2010%25%20of%20which%20were%20still%20in%20use%20last%20summer.%20But%20earning%20a%20modicum%20of%20cool%20in%20what's%20been%20panned%20as%20perhaps%20the%20dorkiest%20market%20in%20tech%20is%20a%20big%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20July%20earnings%20call%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said%20the%20second%20generation%20of%20glasses%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20be%20a%20bigger%20hit%20sooner%20than%20we%20expected%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20AI.%26quot%3B%20People%20were%20buying%20the%20glasses%20quicker%20than%20the%20company%20could%20make%20them%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20market-intelligence%20firm%20International%20Data%20Corporation%20says%20some%20700%2C000%20pairs%20have%20been%20shipped%20since%20last%20October.%20Meta's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ray-bans-have-new-features-smart-glasses-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERay-Bans%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20a%20camera%20and%20speaker%20and%20are%20packed%20with%20AI.%20Updates%20give%20the%20wearer%20real-time%20translation%20if%20someone%20is%20speaking%20with%20them%20in%20Spanish%2C%20English%2C%20French%2C%20or%20Italian%2C%20and%20they%20also%20have%20features%20for%20everyday%20use%2C%20like%20remembering%20where%20you%20parked%20your%20car%20or%20helping%20you%20create%20an%20outfit%20from%20the%20clothes%20in%20your%20closet%20or%20make%20a%20smoothie%20with%20the%20fruits%20in%20front%20of%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20far%20from%20being%20widely%20adopted%2C%20but%20Meta%20hopes%20this%20will%20be%20the%20next%20frontier.%20Glasses%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20natural%20computing%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20The%20Ray-Bans%20also%20have%20the%20benefit%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bjust%20good-looking%20glasses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20crowd%20during%20Meta's%20Connect%202024%20event%2C%20and%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20want%20to%20have%20something%20on%20their%20face%20that%20they're%20proud%20of%20and%20that%20looks%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20important%20to%20overcoming%20the%20cringe%20of%20putting%20a%20computer%20over%20your%20eyes.%20Meta's%20loftier%20goal%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forion-meta-ar-smart-glasses-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOrion%20glasses%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20aren't%20quite%20there.%20They're%20bulkier%20and%20way%20nerdier%20than%20a%20pair%20of%20Ray-Bans%2C%20very%20%26quot%3BDexter's%20Laboratory%26quot%3B-coded%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20a%20more%20approachable%20option%20than%20other%20ski-goggle-like%20headsets%20and%20smart%20glasses.%20Yet%20getting%20people%20into%20the%20Orion%20glasses%20may%20depend%20on%20getting%20people%20comfortable%20with%20smart%20glasses%20generally%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20Ray-Bans%20could%20come%20in.%20They're%20a%20chance%20for%20Meta%20to%20stuff%20its%20AI%20into%20hardware%20and%20keep%20pace%20in%20the%20AI%20arms%20race%20with%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20customers%20aren't%20rushing%20to%20buy%20AI-stuffed%20products%20yet.%20And%20the%20Meta%20Ray-Bans%20make%20it%20even%20easier%20to%20use%20AI%20as%20you%20move%20through%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20no%20hands%20(and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-apple-vision-pro-nightmare-surveillance-privacy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eawkward%20air-pinching%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E)%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20wearables%20are%20a%20tough%20industry.%20The%20VR%20and%20AR%20headset%20market%20has%20slumped%2C%20declining%20by%2054%25%20from%20early%202022%20to%202023%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20IDC.%20The%20number%20of%20VR%20headsets%20shipped%20fell%20by%204%25%20between%202023%20and%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Counterpoint%20Research.%20Despite%20Apple's%20splashy%20release%20of%20its%20Vision%20Pro%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-07-11%2Fapple-s-vision-pro-won-t-cross-500-000-sales-this-year-idc-says%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enot%20expected%20to%20sell%20more%20than%20500%2C000%20devices%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20(in%20comparison%2C%20some%20500%2C000%20iPhones%20are%20sold%20globally%20every%20%3Cem%3Eday%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Its%20%243%2C500%20price%20point%20is%20certainly%20a%20deterrent%20to%20widespread%20adoption%2C%20but%20so%20is%20the%20feasibility%3B%20they're%20clunky%2C%20there%20are%20too%20few%20programs%20made%20for%20them%2C%20and%20they're%20stuck%20among%20a%20niche%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20headsets%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20be%20mass%20market%2C%20ever%2C%20in%20this%20current%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20George%20Jijiashvili%2C%20the%20senior%20principal%20analyst%20of%20games%20at%20the%20research%20firm%20Omdia.%20But%20if%20Meta's%20can%20make%20AI%20work%20in%20a%20way%20that%20combines%20video%20capture%2C%20sound%2C%20and%20location%20context%20together%2C%20the%20glasses%20could%20be%20a%20game%20changer.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20manage%20to%20create%20an%20AI%20solution%20that%20actually%20works%20very%20well%2C%20then%20having%20glasses%20in%20that%20situation%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20sense.%20You%20can%20see%20the%20road%20to%20mass%20adoption%20more%20clearly%20with%20glasses%20than%20with%20VR%20headsets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20Zuckerberg%20hopes%2C%20too.%20Even%20though%20the%20Orion%20glasses%20won't%20be%20sold%20anytime%20soon%2C%20if%20ever%20(Zuckerberg%20acknowledged%20they%20have%20to%20become%20more%20stylish%20and%20affordable)%2C%20he's%20trying%20to%20drum%20up%20excitement%2C%20and%2C%20as%20my%20colleague%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forion-meta-ar-smart-glasses-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeter%20Kafka%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20convince%20the%20world%20that%20he%20can%20build%20the%20future%20of%20computing.%20%26quot%3BThese%20glasses%20exist.%20They%20are%20awesome%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20a%20glimpse%20of%20a%20future%20that%20I%20think%20is%20going%20to%20be%20pretty%20exciting.%26quot%3B%20So%20far%2C%20it's%20been%20hard%20to%20convince%20the%20average%20person%20they%20need%20a%20computer%20strapped%20to%20their%20face.%20But%20a%20fancy%20version%20of%20the%20same%20specs%20worn%20by%20Bob%20Dylan%2C%20Lady%20Gaga%2C%20and%20countless%20other%20celebrities%20who%20arguably%20bring%20more%20cool%20cache%20than%20a%20founder%20wearing%20an%20oversize%20T-shirt%20emblazoned%20with%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-shirt-latin-what-does-it-say-explained-words-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEither%20Zuck%20or%20nothing%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20Latin%20at%20a%20product%20launch%20may%20be%20the%20way%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-new-ray-ban-smart-glasses-apple-vision-pro-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17