0apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20my%20beloved%20neighborhood%2C%20a%20privilege%20I%20recognize%20was%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20many.%20When%20I%20moved%20into%20the%20junior%20two-bedroom%20with%20original%20parquet%20floors%20and%20golden%20western%20light%2C%20I%20felt%20I'd%20stepped%20into%20a%20secure%20future.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20held%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-friends-as-an-adult-stranger-dinner-party-review-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edinner%20parties%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20blonde%20wood%20kitchen%20table.%20I%20filled%20the%20living%20room%20with%20legal%20education%20sessions%20for%20immigrant%20neighbors%20and%20fundraisers%20for%20local%20organizers.%20Daily%2C%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20fire%20escape%20to%20admire%20the%20sunset.%20For%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20apartment%20was%20my%20refuge%2C%20and%20in%20a%20flash%2C%20it%20was%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a117c13-9476-47cc-9781-a7e3e6664c3f%5C%22%3EI%20cremated%20my%20cat%20and%20temporarily%20moved%20blocks%20away%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%2C%20I%20launched%20into%20action.%20I%20paid%20%24200%20to%20cremate%20my%20cat%20and%20have%20her%20remains%20delivered%20to%20my%20office%20in%20a%20plain%20cardboard%20box.%20I%20explained%20to%20the%20gas%20company%20why%20a%20final%20meter%20reading%20was%20impossible.%20I%20moved%20into%20a%20temporary%20rental%20nine%20blocks%20away.%20I%20spent%20hours%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20my%20insurance%20agent%2C%20learning%20the%20technical%20meaning%20of%20%26quot%3Btotal%20loss.%26quot%3B%20I%20filled%20out%20a%20spreadsheet%20calculating%20the%20value%20of%20my%20destroyed%20items%2C%20soothed%20by%20the%20order%20of%20neat%20lines%2C%20columns%2C%20and%20numbers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20grateful%20for%20my%20personal%20property%20coverage%2C%20but%20I%20soon%20found%20that%20many%20of%20my%20neighbors%20had%20no%20insurance%20at%20all%2C%20and%20the%20condo%20board%20woefully%20underinsured%20the%20building%20as%20a%20whole.%20A%20payment%20for%20the%20full%20value%20of%20our%20homes%20was%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I'd%20checked%20all%20the%20bureaucratic%20boxes%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20confront%20my%20loss.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224877f986-6cf6-4a9c-9962-d99d9df0af91%5C%22%3EMy%20friends%20and%20family%20supported%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20sinking%20into%20grief%2C%20my%20community%20threw%20me%20a%20lifeline.%20Fellow%20building%20members%20shared%20support%20and%20commiseration%20via%20group%20text%20as%20we%20scattered%20across%20the%20city.%20My%20parents%20hastily%20arranged%20a%20visit.%20Neighbors%20organized%20a%20collective%20fundraiser%20and%20benefit%20concert.%20A%20colleague%20insisted%20I%20couldn't%20have%20a%20new%20home%20without%20books%2C%20and%20mobilized%20other%20writers%20to%20help%20me%20replace%20my%20favorites.%20My%20old%20classmate's%20father%20sent%20me%20a%20pressure%20cooker.%20An%20ex%20replaced%20my%20gym%20shoes.%20Coworkers%20brought%20food%20to%20my%20door.%20The%20library%20forgave%20fines%20for%20destroyed%20books%20and%20hosted%20a%20communal%20dinner.%20At%20the%20gathering%2C%20Father%20Kevin%2C%20a%20local%20Irish%20Catholic%20priest%20who%20said%20Spanish%20mass%2C%20gave%20a%20blessing%20for%20our%20departed%20pets.%20A%20committed%20agnostic%2C%20I%20was%20grateful%20for%20this%20ritual%2C%20knowing%20my%20Catholic%20grandmother%20would%20have%20been%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friends%20helped%20me%20salvage%20my%20life%20so%20I%20could%20look%20towards%20what%20was%20next.%20In%20disposable%20coveralls%2C%20hard%20hats%2C%20and%20N95%20masks%20to%20protect%20from%20any%20asbestos%20from%20the%20burnt%20roof%2C%20they%20carried%20my%20father's%20mid-century%20desk%2C%20crates%20of%20records%2C%20and%20a%20still%20living%20fiddle%20leaf%20fig%20tree%20down%20five%20flights%20of%20sooty%20stairs.%20I%20swore%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20another%