ore%20than%20550%20million%20shares%20of%20Summit%2C%20a%20roughly%2075%25%20stake.%20The%20company's%20stock%20price%20has%20surged%20by%20over%201%2C100%25%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20lifting%20its%20market%20value%20to%20over%20%2416%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummit%20stock%20jumped%20from%20about%20%2412%20on%20September%206%20to%20a%20record%20high%20of%20%2432%20on%20September%2013%2C%20but%20has%20retreated%20to%20around%20%2423%20since%20then.%20It%20spiked%20after%20the%20company%20released%20late-stage%20trial%20data%20showing%20one%20of%20its%20drugs%2C%20Ivonescimab%2C%20performed%20better%20than%20Merck's%20blockbuster%20Keytruda%20medication%20in%20some%20lung%20cancer%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuggan%20stands%20out%20in%20the%20biotech%20industry%2C%20where%20most%20bosses%20rely%20on%20their%20advanced%20degrees%20to%20navigate%20complex%2C%20jargon-heavy%20medical%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20six%20years%20taking%20classes%20at%20UC%20Santa%20Barbara%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20but%20never%20intended%20to%20get%20a%20degree%20as%20he%20was%20focused%20on%20finding%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-passive-income-strategies-build-wealth-earning-money-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20recently%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fbiotech%2Fhow-a-surfer-who-never-finished-college-became-a-biotech-billionaire-c71eb75f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20included%20investing%20in%20Ethernet%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuggan%20opened%20a%20bakery%20called%20Cookie%20Muncher's%20Paradise%20in%201976%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20then-brother-in-law.%20They%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20luxury%20sandwich%20chain%2C%20grew%20it%20to%2016%20locations%2C%20and%20then%20sold%20it%20for%20about%20%246%20million%20in%201987%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E