ll%20have%20to%20generate%20profits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20whether%20OpenAI%20should%20be%20a%20for-profit%20company%20has%20been%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20for%20one%20very%20vocal%20tech%20industry%20bigwig%20%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20one%20of%20the%20cofounders%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sues-openai-sam-altman-again-why-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevived%20his%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Musk%20is%20now%20accusing%20OpenAI%20of%20deceiving%20him%20into%20co-founding%20the%20firm.%20Musk's%20lawyers%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20Altman%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20con%26quot%3B%20to%20convince%20Musk%20that%20OpenAI%20would%20be%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20would%20build%20a%20safe%20AI%20to%20benefit%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Musk's%20renewed%20legal%20battle%20against%20it%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-fightingwars-alot-of-fronts-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20August%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20said%20about%20Elon's%20initial%20legal%20filing%2C%20which%20was%20subsequently%20withdrawn%2C%20Elon's%20prior%20emails%20continue%20to%20speak%20for%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b31d4d2-2946-4d4d-a2ab-06a047a4b4dc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECritics%20are%20getting%20louder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20switch-up%20to%20its%20corporate%20governance%20leaves%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eroom%20for%20the%20startup%20to%20adhere%20to%20its%20touted%20mission%20of%20benefiting%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20new%20structure%20also%20raises%20new%20risks%20and%20some%20OpenAI%20critics%20say%20it%20gives%20further%20credence%20to%20the%20argument%20that%20%3Ca%20hre