p%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6424fdc-f215-4f83-9953-4226d25f820b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20I%20landed%20in%20Italy%2C%20I%20pretended%20to%20work%2C%20logging%20in%20occasionally%20and%20checking%20emails%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20anything%20particular%20planned%20%E2%80%94%20no%20museum%20entrances%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-do-differently-next-trip-to-italy-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eday%20trips%20booked%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20was%20mostly%20strolling%20around%20the%20lovely%20streets%20of%20Bari%2C%20sitting%20down%20for%20a%20coffee%20or%20gelato%20whenever%20I%20felt%20like%20it%2C%20or%20entering%20a%20museum%20when%20the%20mood%20struck%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20before%20the%20high%20season%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20queues%20or%20needing%20to%20make%20a%20reservation%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20receive%20phone%20calls%20from%20work%20only%20when%20they%20are%20urgent%2C%20and%20we%20use%20email%20for%20things%20of%20lesser%20priority.%20Whenever%20I%20sat%20down%20for%20a%20coffee%20or%20ice%20cream%2C%20I'd%20check%20my%20email%20from%20my%20phone%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20from%20work%20called%20me%20or%20texted%2C%20it%20became%20my%20priority%20to%20respond%20to%20them%20instantly.%20But%20the%20guilt%20and%20stress%20of%20potentially%20getting%20a%20sudden%20call%20made%20it%20hard%20to%20enjoy%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212245855-5afa-49ab-b776-4f2c75dc3a2e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20couldn't%20relax%20and%20constantly%20worried%20about%20work%20interruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%2C%20I%20woke%20up%20early%20before%20the%20sun%20made%20it%20unbearably%20hot%2C%20visited%20some%20nearby%20places%20for%20a%20morning%20coffee%20and%20some%20pastry%2C%20and%20planned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-rome-italy-what-to-skip-tour-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20on%20a%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20grab%20an%20early%20lunch%2C%20and%20do%20some%20work%20in%20a%20restaurant%20or%20bistro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20day%20was%20the%20tipping%20point%20for%20me.%20I%20received%20an%20urgent%20work%20call%20while%20taking%20a%20tour%20of%20Bari%20Castle.%20The%20timing%20couldn't%20have%20been%20worse%2C%20as%20the%20call%20came%20when%20I%20was%20in%20the%20castle%20dungeons%2C%20and%20the%20cell%20signal%20was%20extremely%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20realized%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20I%20went%20pale%20and%20quickly%20ran%20out%20to%20the%20courtyard%20to%20catch%20a%20stronger%20signal.%20Just%20then%2C%20a%20school%20tour%20entered%20the%20same%20courtyard%2C%20and%20the%20noise%20got%20so%20bad%20that%20I%20had%20to%20apologize%20and%20shout%20over%20the%20phone%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20incident%2C%20I%20was%20so%20anxious%20about%20getting%20caught%20while%20quiet%20vacationing%20during%20work%20hours%20that%20I%20changed%20my%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1285364-1997-4627-9b56-55b2be9c3e16%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20working%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20during%20my%20quiet%20vacation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20working%20around%207%20a.m.%20local%20time%20and%20aimed%20to%20finish%20by%202%20p.m.%20when%20I%20felt%20like%20Italians%20were%20just%20waking%20up%20to%20start%20their%20day.%20This%20was%20a%20game%20changer.%20I%20could%20finally%20relax%20and%20get%20to%20know%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fitaly-things-to-never-do-there-according-to-local-photos-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20work%20hanging%20over%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20putting%20in%20enough%20time%20to%20ensure%20my%20work%20was%20done%20properly%20and%20there%20were%20no%20problems.%20I