ut%20leaving%20Bangladesh%20once%20I%20go%20there%20is%20dangerous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shakib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20Shakib%20is%20unable%20to%20feature%20in%20Mirpur%20Test%20next%20month%2C%20the%20second%20and%20final%20game%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%20against%20India%2C%20starting%20in%20Kanpur%20on%20Friday%2C%20could%20be%20his%20last%20game%20for%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20longer%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20fitting%20to%20conclude%20my%20Test%20career%20in%20front%20of%20my%20home%20fans.%20Bangladesh%20cricket%20has%20given%20me%20so%20much%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20give%20my%20last%20in%20this%20format%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib's%20Test%20debut%2C%20interestingly%2C%20came%20against%20India%20in%20Chattogram%20back%20in%20May%202007%2C%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20play%2070%20Tests%20for%20Bangladesh.%20He%20has%20amassed%204%2C600%20runs%2C%20including%20five%20centuries%20and%2031%20half-centuries%2C%20making%20him%20the%20third-highest%20run-scorer%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Test%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20is%20Bangladesh's%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20with%20242%20scalps.%20He%20remains%20the%20only%20bowler%20from%20his%20country%20to%20surpass%20the%20200-wicket%20mark%20in%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20his%20Test%20career%2C%20Shakib%20also%20confirmed%20his%20plans%20to%20retire%20from%20ODI%20cricket%20after%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20set%20to%20be%20held%20early%20that%20year.%20With%20a%20career%20spanning%20over%2017%20years%2C%20Shakib%20has%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Bangladesh's%20rise%20on%20the%20international%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Champions%20Trophy%20will%20mark%20his%20last%20appearance%20in%20a%20major%20global%20tournament%20for%20the%20Tigers%2C%20after%20which%20he%20will%20retire%20from%20all%20formats%20of%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727341260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fn8omsdk8_shakib-al-hasan_625x300_21_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fshakib-al-hasan-says-2nd-test-vs-india-in-kanpur-will-be-his-last-if-he-doesnt-get-farewell-match-at-home-6653651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20all-rounder%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20against%20India%20in%20Kanpur%20can%20be%20his%20last%20if%20he%20does%20not%20get%20a%20farewell%20match%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fshakib-al-hasan-says-2nd-test-vs-india-in-kanpur-will-be-his-last-if-he-doesnt-get-farewell-match-at-home-6653651%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%20%7C%20The%20Karnataka%20Conundrum%3A%20The%20Road%20Ahead%20For%20A%20Chastened%20Siddaramaiah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20court%20setback%20for%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20means%20he%20can%20be%20prosecuted%20in%20a%20land%20scam%20that%20threatens%20to%20upend%20his%20government%20and%20his%20long%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20rejected%20Siddaramaiah's%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Governor's%20August%2016%20order%20sanctioning%20action%20against%20him%20in%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%26quot%3B%20allotment%20of%2014%20housing%20plots%20to%20his%20wife%20Parvathi%20in%20Mysuru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20was%20expecting%20a%20favourable%20verdict%20in%20the%20MUDA%20(Mysore%20Urban%20Development%20Authority)%20land%20scam%20case%2C%20dubbed%20by%20many%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20%26quot%3BMUDA%20muddle%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Siddaramaiah%20faces%20resignation%20calls%2C%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20-%20and%20its%20Delhi%20leadership%20-%20is%20struggling%20with%20damage%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20batted%20away%20the%20demands%20for%20his%20resignation%2C%20asserting%20that%20he%20will%20fight%20the%20case%20and%20win.%20He%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20weaken%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20his%20position%20is%20wobbly%2C%20perhaps%20his%20biggest%20threat%20is%20in-house%20-%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20his%20deputy%20and%20rival%2C%20who%20has%20never%20masked%20his%20ambition%20to%20hold%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20Options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20single%20judge%20bench%20of%20Justice%20M%20Nagaprasanna%20said%20that%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20accept%20that%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20not%20'behind%20the%20curtain'%20during%20the%20MUDA%20land%20deal%2C%20in%20which%20his%20family%20allegedly%20benefitted%20approximately%20Rs%2056%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20facts%20narrated%20in%20the%20petition%20would%20undoubtedly%20require%20an%20investigation...(given)%20that%20the%20beneficiary%20of%20all%20these%20acts%20is%20not%20anybody%20outside%2C%20but%20the%20petitioner's%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20Justice%20Nagaprasanna%2C%20endorsing%20Governor%20Gehlot's%20sanction%20for%20prosecution%20under%20Section%2017A%20of%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20and%20Section%20218%20of%20the%20new%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor's%20sanction%20came%20in%20response%20to%20requests%20from%20activists%20TJ%20Abraham%2C%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20SP%20and%20Snehamayi%20Krishna.%20The%20court%20order%20allows%20the%20three%20RTI%20activists%20to%20approach%20an%20anti-corruption%20agency%20such%20as%20the%20Karnataka%20Lokayukta%20police%20to%20seek%20a%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Karnataka%20Special%20Court%20has%20now%20ordered%20a%20Lokayukta%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20can%20approach%20a%20larger%20bench%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20Judge%20Nagaprasanna's%20decision.%20His%20legal%20team%20is%20weighing%20the%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress's%20Dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20this%20crisis%20is%20a%20test%20of%20its%20political%20acuity.%20If%20it%20asks%20Siddaramaiah%20to%20go%2C%20it%20invites%20more%20opposition%20attacks.%20If%20it%20doesn't%2C%20it%20loses%20moral%20high%20ground%20and%20also%20sets%20itself%20up%20for%20political%20instability%2C%20with%20Siddaramaiah%20as%20potential%20troublemaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20delicate%20high%20wire%20act%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20also%20because%20any%20forced%20leadership%20change%20may%20alienate%20the%20AHINDA%20(a%20Kannada%20acronym%20for%20Minorities%2C%20OBC%2C%20and%20Dalits)%20voters%20who%20form%20Siddaramaiah's%20support%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20has%20the%20support%20of%20party%20MLAs%2C%20more%20than%20Shivakumar.%20But%20if%20the%20Congress%20considers%20a%20third%20option%2C%20Shivakumar%20will%20cause%20trouble.%20For%20now%2C%20Shivakumar%20is%20publicly%20supporting%20Siddaramaiah%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20'unity'.%20The%20party%20%26quot%3Bstands%20with%20Siddaramaiah%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20calling%20the%20cases%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20of%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B%20against%20rival%20parties%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20close%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20say%20Siddaramaiah%20is%20a%20fighter%20and%20that%20he%20has%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20high%20command.%20And%20that%20he%20will%20never%20capitulate%20or%20submit%20to%20%26quot%3Bintimidation%20or%20conspiracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20has%20weakened%20the%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20a%20state%20it%20won%20last%20year%2C%20with%20the%20focus%20shifting%20from%20governance%20to%20corruption%20allegations.%20With%20Siddaramaiah%20entangled%20in%20legal%20battles%2C%20the%20government's%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20neglected%20and%20mismanaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20of%20now%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20will%20continue%20as%20chief%20minister.%20The%20question%20of%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20may%20not%20arise.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20party%20might%20face%20some%20disturbances%20within%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Harish%20Ramaswamy%2C%20political%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20the%20question%20is%20how%20it%20controls%20its%20cadres%20and%20MLAs%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20Upbeat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20BJP%2C%20still%20smarting%20from%20its%20defeat%20in%20the%202023%20state%20election%2C%20is%20aggressively%20demanding%20Siddaramaiah's%20removal%20and%20an%20impartial%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20the%20CBI.%20The%20party's%20Karnataka%20ally%20JD(S)%20is%20also%20elated.%20Taking%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20referred%20to%20Siddaramaiah%20as%20%26quot%3BWhitener%20Ramaiah%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bblack%20spots%26quot%3B%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20chastened%20Siddaramaiah%20facing%20heat%20from%20a%20rejuvenated%20opposition%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20verdict%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20court's%20decision%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20BJP%20state%20president%20BY%20Vijayendra%20and%20opposition%20leader%20R%20Ashok%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20they%20called%20for%20Siddaramaiah%20to%20step%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Court's%20decision%20confirms%20the%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20I%20urge%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20respect%20the%20legal%20process.%20The%20High%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20Governor's%20order%20for%20prosecution.%20It%20is%20now%20time%20for%20Siddaramaiah%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20post%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20state%20chief%20BY%20Vijayendra%2C%20the%20son%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20BS%20Yediyurappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20may%20feel%20the%20impact%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20but%20it%20has%20to%20strategise%20for%20the%20long%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20will%20likely%20have%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20the%20upcoming%20by-elections%20in%20three%20seats%20-%20Channapatna%2C%20from%20where%20JD(S)'%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20was%20sitting%20MLA%3B%20Shiggaon%20vacated%20by%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20of%20BJP%2C%20and%20Sandur%20vacated%20by%20E%20Tukaram%20of%20Congress.%20All%20three%20were%20elected%20to%20parliament%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dent%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20soon%20be%20evident%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20far%20the%20opposition%20capitalising%20on%20the%20court%20decision.%20Let's%20see%20who%20has%20the%20upper%20hand%20in%20this%20political%20battle%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ramaswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727340960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F7qosjpcg_siddaramaiah_625x300_26_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-karnataka-conundrum-the-road-ahead-for-a-chastened-siddaramaiah-in-muda-scam-case-6653812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20huge%20court%20setback%20