%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20of%20the%20legend%E2%80%99s%20body%20of%20work%20is%20celebrated%20under%20his%20name%20Hanif%2C%20if%20you%20should%20ever%20stumble%20across%20a%20brilliant%20painting%20by%20%E2%80%98Daku%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Guerrilla%E2%80%99%2C%20know%20that%20it%20finds%20its%20roots%20in%20the%20same%20brush.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Gujarat-born%20Hanif%20and%20his%20pseudonyms%20created%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F187060%2Fchennai-street-sustainable-homes-green-award-tamil-nadu-govt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emovement%20out%20of%20street%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20one%20that%20shows%20no%20signs%20of%20slowing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20love%20affair%20of%20Hanif%20Kureshi%20and%20his%20brush%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShock%20waves%20spread%20through%20the%20art%20community%20on%20Sunday%20when%20St%2Bart%20India%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Instagram%20page%20announced%20the%20death%20of%20their%20beloved%20co-founder%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20with%20deep%20sadness%20that%20we%20share%20the%20passing%20of%20Hanif%20Kureshi%2C%20our%20beloved%20co-founder%2C%20artistic%20director%20and%20artist.%20We%20are%20gutted%20and%20at%20a%20loss%20of%20words.%20Hanif%20was%20a%20gifted%20mentor%2C%20collaborator%2C%20friend%2C%20father%2C%20and%20husband.%20His%20vision%20and%20charisma%20helped%20shape%20the%20landscape%20of%20public%20art%20in%20India%20with%20the%20countless%20projects%20he%20has%20contributed%20to.%20He%20was%20dedicated%20to%20nurturing%20a%20community%20of%20artists%2C%20designers%2C%20and%20creatives%20who%20trusted%20him%20with%20loyal%20guidance.%20He%20was%20a%20pioneering%20figure%20for%20graffiti%20and%20street%20art%20with%20his%20tags%20spread%20across%20cities%20he%20travelled%20to.%20It%20has%20been%20an%20honour%20for%20the%20St%2BArt%2C%20XXL%2C%20and%20Guerrilla%