%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-cant-be-released-yet-censor-decision-in-a-week-6599688%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBut%20Creative%20Freedom%3F%26quot%3B%20Court's%20Deadline%20For%20Kangana's%20'Emergency'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20the%20CBFC%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20sit%20on%20the%20fence%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20decision.%20Let's%20see%20what%20the%20revising%20committee%20says%2C%20be%20it%20deciding%20to%20release%20or%20not%2C%20take%20a%20decision.%20Have%20the%20courage%20to%20say%20that%20the%20film%20should%20not%20be%20released.%20We%20will%20appreciate%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20CBFC%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinav%20Chandrachud%2C%20the%20censor%20board's%20counsel%2C%20told%20the%20court%20some%20scenes%20show%20a%20polarising%20figure%20cutting%20a%20deal%20with%20political%20parties.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20see%20if%20this%20is%20factually%20accurate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20while%20also%20noting%20there%20is%20no%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20angle%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20matter%20came%20up%20before%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20when%20two%20Sikh%20organisations%20filed%20a%20PIL.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20CBFC%20told%20the%20court%20the%20movie%20had%20not%20been%20issued%20a%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-stuck-in-massive-row-what-are-the-objections-6487046%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%20Stuck.%20What%20Are%20The%20Objections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20disposed%20of%20that%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ranaut%20-%20who%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20a%20spat%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20comments%20about%20the%20party's%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20and%20Soni