w-sanctioned-goods-are-getting-into-russia-13221889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sanctions%20on%20Russia%20were%20introduced%20two%20years%20ago%20shortly%20after%20the%20start%20of%20the%20country's%20Ukrainian%20invasion.%20The%20purpose%3F%20To%20limit%20the%20Russian%C2%A0war%20machine%20and%20starve%20Russian%20oligarchs%20of%20access%20to%20luxury%20items.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhow-sanctioned-goods-are-getting-into-russia-13221889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhow-sanctioned-goods-are-getting-into-russia-13221889%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhow-sanctioned-goods-are-getting-into-russia-13221889%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Contraceptive%20Day%3A%20Why%20This%20Couple%20Chose%20Vasectomy%20as%20Their%20Preferred%20Contraceptive%20Method%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20years%20into%20their%20marriage%2C%20Rajesh%20Raman%20(%3Cem%3Ename%20changed%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20finance%20professional%20and%20his%20wife%20Meera%20(%3Cem%3Ename%20changed%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20medical%20professional%2C%20began%20to%20seriously%20contemplate%20the%20idea%20of%20not%20having%20children%20at%20all.%20After%20deliberating%20on%20the%20matter%20for%20two%20years%2C%20they%20decided%20that%20Rajesh%20would%20get%20a%20vasectomy%20done.%20%3Cem%3E(Representational%20Image%20above%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FGround%20Picture)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20probably%20among%20the%20few%20couples%20in%20this%20country%20who%20decided%20to%20take%20this%20step%20without%20having%20children.%20About%20six%20years%20into%20our%20marriage%2C%20we%20started%20discussing%20that%20maybe%20having%20children%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20our%20life%20goals.%20Besides%20my%20corporate%20job%2C%20I%20also%20work%20as%20a%20life%20coach%20in%20a%20startup%20I%20run%20with%20my%20wife.%20I%20work%20with%20more%20than%202%2C000%20people%20on%20various%20issues%20like%20abuse%2C%20relationship%20management%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367326%2Ftoxic-workplaces-solutions-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajesh%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20support%20our%20collective%20vision%20of%20creating%20a%20wider%20impact%20in%20society%2C%20we%20felt%20that%20maybe%20having%20our%20biological%20child%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20our%20plan.%20After%20deliberating%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20I%20got%20a%20vasectomy%20done%20in%202020%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2037-year-old%20based%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20their%20decision%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20Rajesh%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20having%20a%20child%20is%20at%20least%20a%2021-year%20investment%20of%20your%20time.%20As%20parents%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20dedicate%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20time%20and%20energy.%20As%20a%20parent%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20top%20priority%20to%20raise%20a%20child%20to%20be%20the%20best%20that%20they%20can%20be.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20tremendous%20responsibility%20and%20you%20need%20to%20do%20justice%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20arriving%20at%20this%20decision%20to%20not%20have%20children%2C%20Rajesh%20and%20Meera%20spoke%20to%20many%20people%20from%20academics%20to%20spiritualists%20who%20helped%20them%20understand%20that%20there%20are%20myriad%20ways%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20a%20caregiver%20other%20than%20becoming%20a%20biological%20parent.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20ways%20to%20fulfil%20the%20duty%20of%20a%20caregiver%20besides%20being%20parents%20to%20a%20child.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20we%20are%20running%20away%20from%20the%20responsibility%20%5Bof%20becoming%20parents%5D.%20It%20is%20just%20that%20we%20seek%20to%20devote%20our%20responsibility%20and%20time%20to%20a%20wider%20set%20of%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20how%20to%20%E2%80%98seal%20the%20deal%E2%80%99%20on%20their%20decision%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20Rajesh%20and%20Meera%20spoke%20to%20doctors%20and%20explored%20the%20various%20contraceptive%20options%20before%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20some%20temporary%20and%20permanent%20options%20available.%20Funnily%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20contraception%20options%20are%20diverted%20towards%20females%20like%20copper%20IUDs%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298313%2Fdr-nitya-anand-developed-saheli-worlds-first-non-steroidal-contraceptive-pill-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoral%20contraceptives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20etc.%20If%20they%E2%80%99re%20looking%20long%20term%2C%20women%20have%20to%20undergo%20tubal%20ligation%2C%20which%20is%20a%20cumbersome%20medical%20procedure%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20four-week%20average%20recovery%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVasectomy%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20simpler%20procedure%20with%20a%20faster%20recovery%20process.%20We%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20and%20watched%20many%20testimonials%20online.%20We%20also%20spoke%20to%20a%20few%20doctors%20who%20have%20performed%20vasectomies%20and%20people%20who%20have%20undergone%20it.%20Taking%20into%20account%20their%20inputs%2C%20we%20felt%20that%20a%20vasectomy%20is%20the%20safest%2C%20most%20permanent%20and%20least%20complicated%20procedure%20with%20little%20to%20no%20side%20effects.%20This%20was%20also%20a%20medical%20decision%20besides%20a%20personal%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vasectomy%20is%20a%20safe%20choice%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367517%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20Rajesh%20and%20Meera%20spoke%20to%20doctors%20and%20explored%20the%20various%20contraceptive%20options%20before%20them%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FMotortion%20Films)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20their%20parents%20and%20relatives%20react%20to%20this%20decision%20to%20get%20a%20vasectomy%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20those%20two%20years%20%5Bbefore%20getting%20a%20vasectomy%5D%2C%20Rajesh%20and%20Meera%20had%20very%20open%20and%20transparent%20discussions%20with%20their%20respective%20families%20about%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20have%20children.%20Thankfully%2C%20their%20parents%20were%20completely%20aligned%20with%20Rajesh%20and%20Meera%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20surprised%20them%20was%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20doctors.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20went%20to%20a%20few%20doctors%20%5Burologists%5D%20who%20perform%20vasectomies%2C%20we%20were%20turned%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20they%20were%20not%20sure%20that%20we%20were%20a%20couple%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20furnish%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208937%2Fhow-to-get-a-marriage-certificate-india-steps-to-follow-procedures-documents-required-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarriage%20certificate%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20a%20young%20couple%20opting%20for%20a%20permanent%20sterilisation%20procedure%20without%20having%20children.%20Some%20doctors%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98naughty%E2%80%99%20here.%20We%20argued%20that%20this%20decision%20came%20after%20much%20deliberation%20and%20thought.%20After%20an%20extended%20search%2C%20we%20finally%20found%20a%20doctor%20who%20was%20ready%20to%20do%20the%20procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERajesh%E2%80%99s%20experience%20with%20the%20vasectomy%20procedure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rajesh%20describes%20his%20experience%20of%20getting%20a%20vasectomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20simple%20vasectomy%20requires%20cutting%20off%20and%20sealing%20the%20vas%20deferens%2C%20which%20are%20the%20two%20tubes%20that%20carry%20the%20sperm%20from%20the%20testicles%20to%20the%20urethra%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20a%20permanent%20form%20of%20male%20birth%20control.%20The%20entire%20procedure%20can%20be%20done%20either%20on%20general%20or%20local%20anaesthesia.%20For%20my%20%5Bwith%20scalpel%5D%20vasectomy%2C%20I%20went%20with%20local%20anaesthesia.%20The%20procedure%20took%20about%2015%20minutes.%20It%20was%20very%20quick.%20I%20felt%20very%20little%20pain%20during%20the%20procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20had%20Meera%2C%20a%20doctor%2C%20witness%20the%20procedure%20since%20she%20knew%20the%20urologist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20procedure%2C%20you%20may%20know%20when%20the%20doctor%20cuts%20your%20vas%20deferens%20because%20you%20feel%20a%20sensation.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20they%E2%80%99re%20sealing%20it%20off%2C%20you%20will%20again%20feel%20a%20certain%20sensation%20and%20not%20any%20sort%20of%20intense%20pain%20because%20you%E2%80%99re%20under%20anaesthesia.%20You%E2%80%99re%20then%20quickly%20stitched%20up%20and%20then%20put%20on%20a%20course%20of%20painkillers%20for%20the%20next%20four%20or%20five%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%2C%20adding%20that%20post-procedure%2C%20he%20felt%20slight%20discomfort%20while%20sitting%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20recommend%20getting%20the%20procedure%20done%20on%20a%20Friday%20so%20that%20you%20get%20your%20weekend%20off.%20You%20can%20work%20from%20home%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20you%20are%20almost%20back%20to%20normal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajesh%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoctors%20ask%20you%20not%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20activity%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks.%20The%20first%20time%20you%20ejaculate%20after%20the%20procedure%2C%20you%20might%20find%20a%20bit%20of%20blood%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20no%20reason%20to%20get%20freaked%20out.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20normal%20thing.%20After%2060%20days%2C%20you%20will%20need%20to%20do%20a%20sperm%20count%20test%2Fsemen%20analysis%20where%20the%20result%20should%20be%20zero.%20Doctors%20also%20do%20a%20biopsy%20of%20the%20piece%20of%20vas%20deferens%20that%20has%20been%20cut%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20the%20procedure%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fou4OwCCjux4%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20receiving%20the%20results%20of%20his%20sperm%20count%20test%2C%20Rajesh%20recalls%20a%20funny%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%20the%20report%20comes%20four%20hours%20after%20the%20test.%20So%2C%20I%20called%20the%20lab%20asking%20for%20the%20results%20and%20a%20lady%20on%20the%20other%20line%20of%20the%20phone%20said%20that%20my%20report%20had%20come%20out%20wrong%20and%20was%20unwilling%20to%20get%20into%20the%20specifics.%20Then%20my%20wife%20called%20and%20pressed%20her%20on%20the%20results.%20She%20was%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%20my%20god%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20very%20sorry%20to%20say%20your%20husband%E2%80%99s%20sperm%20count%20is%20zero.%E2%80%99%20That%20lady%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20this%20was%20good%20news%20to%20us%20and%20she%20was%20relieved%20after%20my%20wife%20explained%20that%20a%20vasectomy%20had%20been%20done.%20We%20still%20get%20a%20nice%20laugh%20out%20of%20recalling%20this%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20men%20on%20board%20for%20contraception%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20problems%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20family%20programme%20initiatives%20is%20that%20men%20are%20hesitant%20or%20unwilling%20to%20undergo%20a%20vasectomy%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20they%20put%20their%20wives%2Fpartners%20through%20longer%2C%20more%20difficult%20and%20more%20painful%20procedures%20that%20require%20a%20longer%20recovery%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20Muttreja%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Population%20Foundation%20of%20India%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFamily%20planning%20is%20a%20shared%20responsibility%20between%20partners.%20Involving%20men%20in%20family%20planning%20programmes%20can%20foster%20better%20spousal%20communication%2C%20promote%20gender-equitable%20attitudes%2C%20and%20increase%20the%20uptake%20of%20family%20planning%20methods.%20Despite%20this%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20family%20planning%20programme%20shows%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20male%20involvement.%20Currently%2C%20the%20public%20health%20system%20provides%20only%20two%20male-specific%20contraceptive%20options%3A%20condoms%20and%20male%20sterilisation%20(vasectomy).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS)%205%20(2019-21)%20data%20showed%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20uptake%20of%20condoms%20(from%205.6%25%20in%202015-16%20to%209.5%25%20in%202019-21)%2C%20condoms%20and%20male%20sterilisation%20contributed%20only%2017%25%20and%201%25%20respectively%20in%20the%20method%20mix.%20Although%20male%20sterilisation%20is%20a%20simpler%20procedure%20compared%20to%20female%20sterilisation%2C%20female%20sterilisation%20remains%20the%20most%20popular%20modern%20contraceptive%20method.%20The%20weightage%20of%20female%20sterilisation%20in%20total%20use%20of%20modern%20contraceptives%20for%20family%20planning%20was%2067%25%20in%202019-21%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-3-1727271932.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stamp%20printed%20in%20India%20shows%20Family%2C%20Family%20Planning%2C%20circa%201987.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-3-1727271932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-3-1727271932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-3-1727271932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-3-1727271932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-3-1727271932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20stamp%20printed%20in%20India%20shows%20Family%2C%20Family%20Planning%2C%20circa%201987%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FBoris15)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20do%20Indian%20men%20remain%20hesitant%20or%20unwilling%20to%20undergo%20procedures%20like%20vasectomy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Poonam%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20parts%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%20men%20do%20not%20participate%20in%20discussions%20and%20informed%20decision-making%20about%20family%20planning%2C%20and%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20women%20to%20use%20contraceptives.%20NFHS%205%20data%20reveals%20that%20more%20than%20one-third%20(35%25)%20of%20men%20believe%20that%20contraception%20is%20women%E2%80%99s%20business.%20This%20mindset%20has%20resulted%20in%20limited%20male%20involvement%20in%20family%20planning%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COther%20contributing%20factors%20include%20limited%20awareness%20of%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%2C%20insufficient%20knowledge%20about%20effective%20contraceptive%20methods%2C%20and%20the%20persistence%20of%20myths%20and%20misconceptions.%20Gender%20inequality%2C%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20cultural%20norms%2C%20continues%20to%20hinder%20effective%20male%20engagement%20in%20family%20planning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20we%20overcome%20some%20of%20these%20barriers%20and%20get%20more%20men%20involved%20in%20contraception%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShattering%20myths%20surrounding%20male%20contraception%20and%20vasectomies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20major%20myths%20and%20misconceptions%20surrounding%20male%20contraception%2C%20particularly%20vasectomy%2C%20contribute%20to%20its%20low%20acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COne%20prevalent%20misconception%20is%20that%20vasectomy%20leads%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20virility%2C%20libido%2C%20etc%2C%20despite%20medical%20evidence%20showing%20no%20impact%20on%20sexual%20function.%20Another%20myth%20is%20that%20the%20procedure%20is%20irreversible%2C%20whereas%20vasectomies%20are%20often%20reversible%2C%20with%20the%20success%20rates%20depending%20on%20timing%20and%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Poonam.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20there%20is%20a%20widespread%20belief%20that%20family%20planning%20is%20solely%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%2C%20reinforced%20by%20traditional%20gender%20roles.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20male%20sterilisation%20accounting%20for%20only%201%25%2C%20compared%20to%2067%25%20female%20sterilisation%20in%20the%20method%20mix%20as%20per%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS-5)%20data%2C%20highlighting%20the%20stark%20gender%20disparity%20in%20contraceptive%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-1-1727272351.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vasectomy%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-1-1727272351.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-1-1727272351-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-1-1727272351-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-1-1727272351-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-1-1727272351-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367547%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20In%20India%2C%20major%20myths%20and%20misconceptions%20surrounding%20male%20contraception%2C%20particularly%20vasectomy%2C%20contribute%20to%20its%20low%20acceptance.%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FYuriY%20K)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202019%20conversation%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F204903%2Findia-male-contraceptive-safe-methods-injection-innovation-iit-invention-risug%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20infertility%20specialist%20working%20for%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNearly%2C%20the%20entire%20burden%20of%20the%20family%20planning%20programme%20is%20carried%20by%20women.%20This%20is%20because%20of%20social%20mindset%2C%20dubious%20claims%20that%20vasectomy%20reduces%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20virility%20and%20ability%20to%20work%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20other%20options.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20urologist%20who%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20says%20that%20men%20have%20the%20option%20of%20getting%20a%20traditional%20(with%20scalpel)%20and%20no-scalpel%20vasectomy.%20While%20both%20options%20are%20safe%2C%20he%20argues%20that%20no-scalpel%20vasectomy%20is%20the%20preferred%20choice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20safest%2C%20most%20painless%2C%20bloodless%2C%20and%20easiest%20modes%20of%20family%20planning%20is%20no-scalpel%20vasectomy%20for%20men.%20This%20procedure%20has%20no%20adverse%20impact%20on%20your%20sex%20life.%20You%20get%20the%20same%20enjoyment%20out%20of%20sex%20as%20you%20did%20earlier.%20If%20a%20surgery%20which%20takes%20a%20few%20minutes%20allows%20you%20and%20your%20family%20to%20secure%20themselves%20against%20unwanted%20pregnancies%2C%20a%20no-scalpel%20vasectomy%20is%20a%20great%20option.%20Also%2C%20a%20no-scalpel%20vasectomy%20is%20reversible.%20For%20some%20reason%2C%20if%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20want%20a%20child%2C%20a%20doctor%20can%20undertake%20a%20procedure%20to%20reverse%20its%20effects%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20urologist.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7bAO_mFbwmY%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20own%20experience%2C%20Rajesh%20states%20unequivocally%20that%20vasectomy%20does%20not%20affect%20his%20sexual%20activity.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20spend%20on%20condoms%20again.%20And%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20plan%20when%20you%20can%20have%20sex.%20Getting%20a%20vasectomy%20has%20zero%20impact%20on%20your%20sex%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20getting%20a%20vasectomy%20has%20improved%20my%20sexual%20performance%20because%20I%20am%20in%20a%20better%20%5Bmind%5D%20space.%20There%20is%20no%20reduction%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20enjoyment%20I%20can%20get%20from%20sex.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20changes%20physiologically%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20100%25%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20more%20men%20involved%20in%20contraception%20and%20family%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20we%20get%20more%20men%20involved%20in%20contraception%20and%20family%20planning%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20far%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20has%20taken%20some%20steps%20to%20mainstream%20men%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20family%20planning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Poonam%2C%20these%20include%2C%20%E2%80%9CVasectomy%20fortnight%20(every%20November)%2C%20installation%20of%20condom%20boxes%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20health%20care%20facilities%2C%20IIC%2FBCC%20campaigns%20to%20promote%20male%20contraceptives%2C%20counselling%20of%20men%20on%20contraceptives%20by%20involvement%20of%20ASHAs%2C%20distribution%20of%20Nayi%20Pehel%20kit%20containing%20condoms%20for%20newlyweds%2C%20and%20organisation%20of%20the%20Saas%20Bahu%20Pati%20Sammelan%20to%20promote%20male%20engagement%20under%20Mission%20Parivar%20Vikas%20programme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20initiatives%20have%20increased%20awareness%20and%20demand%20for%20family%20planning.%20But%20there%20is%20much%20more%20to%20be%20achieved%20to%20realise%20gender%20equity%20fully%20and%20shared%20responsibility%20in%20family%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vasectomy%20for%20Indian%20family%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CBy%20engaging%20men%20as%20equal%20partners%20in%20family%20planning%2C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FMaster%20of%20Stocks)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAddressing%20stereotypes%20and%20encouraging%20men%20to%20view%20family%20planning%20as%20a%20shared%20responsibility%20requires%20a%20comprehensive%20approach.%20Public%20health%20systems%2C%20family%20planning%20programmes%2C%20and%20communication%20strategies%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20promote%20male%20involvement%20actively.%20By%20engaging%20men%20as%20equal%20partners%20in%20family%20planning%2C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20argues%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sustained%20effort%20in%20behaviour%20change%20communication%2C%20combined%20with%20active%20on-ground%20engagement%20with%20men%2C%20is%20essential%20while%20promoting%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20decision-making%20autonomy.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20shifting%20mindsets%20and%20addressing%20stereotypes%20to%20empower%20women%20in%20making%20informed%20health%20decisions%2C%20while%20also%20fostering%20open%20communication%20between%20spouses.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20initiate%20these%20efforts%20early%20by%20engaging%20adolescents%20in%20discussions%20about%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20and%20rights.%20Additionally%2C%20strategic%20engagement%20is%20needed%20to%20encourage%20men%20to%20consider%20vasectomy%20as%20a%20viable%20family%20planning%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20get%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20male%20engagement%20intervention%20needs%20a%20multi-sectoral%20approach.%20Education%2C%20age%20at%20marriage%2C%20health-seeking%20behaviour%2C%20and%20socio-cultural%20norms%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20simultaneously%20and%20concurrently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20two%20steps%20she%20recommends%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrontline%20health%20workers%20(ASHAs%2C%20ANMs)%20must%20be%20supported%20and%20male%20health%20workers%20must%20be%20added%20to%20supplement%20the%20existing%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiven%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20present%20emphasis%20on%20strengthening%20counselling%20at%20hospitals%2C%20an%20increased%20thrust%20on%20couples%20counselling%20and%20follow-ups%20is%20likely%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20is%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20couples%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367538%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FIndianFaces%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%E2%80%99s%20effort%20to%20engage%20male%20peer%20educators%20as%20part%20of%20the%20RKSK%20(Rashtriya%20Kishor%20Swasthya%20Karyakram)%20programme%20is%20a%20move%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20private%20partners%2C%20to%20involve%20men%20in%20this%20process%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined.%20Innovative%20ways%20to%20ensure%20this%20under%20existing%20PPP%20(public-private%20partnership)%20and%20social%20franchising%20models%20will%20positively%20impact%20health%20and%20family%20planning%20at%20the%20community%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20male%20participation%20crucial%20in%20family%20planning%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20believes%20that%20if%20you%20already%20have%20a%20child%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20intend%20to%20have%20another%2C%20getting%20a%20vasectomy%20is%20a%20must%20so%20that%20you%20can%20move%20on%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20have%20children%20at%20all%2C%20my%20suggestion%20is%20to%20take%2018%20months%20as%20a%20couple%20to%20discuss%20this%20in%20honest%20detail%2C%20do%20the%20research%2C%20talk%20to%20experts%2C%20understand%20what%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20parent%20and%20have%20those%20delicate%20conversations%20with%20your%20family.%20Once%20you%20are%20clear%20about%20this%20decision%2C%20get%20the%20procedure%20done%20and%20move%20on%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20Poonam%20notes%20that%20the%20discourse%20on%20the%20engagement%20of%20men%20as%20partners%20in%20accessing%20family%20planning%20and%20health%20services%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20contraceptive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMale%20participation%20is%20about%20being%20responsible%20and%20respecting%20equality%20rather%20than%20just%20about%20decision-making.%20It%20should%20extend%20to%20the%20role%20of%20men%20as%20enablers%20and%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ensuring%20dignity%2C%20equal%20voice%2C%20and%20reproductive%20rights%20for%20women.%20Male%20participation%20should%20not%20mean%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20decision-making%20powers%20are%20encumbered%2C%20and%20women%20are%20forced%20to%20accept%20men%E2%80%99s%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20reveal%20that%20men%20often%20control%20contraception%20decision-making%20and%20decision%20of%20contraception%20of%20female%20partners%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20prevalence%2