0mother%20claims%20her%20death%20was%20caused%20by%20overwhelming%20work%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20had%20only%20begun%20her%20career%20at%20the%20firm%20in%20March%202024%2C%20but%20according%20to%20her%20family%20and%20colleagues%2C%20she%20was%20quickly%20burdened%20with%20excessive%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20workload%2C%20new%20environment%2C%20and%20long%20hours%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20her%20physically%2C%20mentally%20and%20emotionally.%20She%20began%20experiencing%20anxiety%2C%20sleeplessness%2C%20and%20stress%20but%20kept%20pushing%20herself%2C%20believing%20that%20hard%20work%20and%20perseverance%20were%20the%20keys%20to%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anita%20added%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragic%20death%20of%2026-year-old%20Anna%20has%20cast%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20fostering%20a%20healthy%20work%20culture%20and%20implementing%20policies%20that%20promote%20a%20supportive%20environment.%20Anna%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20case%2C%20as%20the%20flood%20of%20grief%20and%20anger%20on%20social%20media%20reveals.%20Many%20people%20have%20come%20forward%2C%20sharing%20their%20own%20experiences%20with%20toxic%20workplaces%2C%20the%20stress%20they%20endured%2C%20and%20how%20it%20led%20to%20health%20issues%20or%20even%20forced%20them%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%2C%20requesting%20details%20about%20the%20investigation%E2%80%99s%20findings%20and%20the%20measures%20being%20taken%20to%20prevent%20further%20loss%20of%20young%20lives%20due%20to%20work-related%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.%20chasing%20impractical%20targets%20and%20timelines%20is%20resulting%20in%20grave%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20of%20the%20employees.%20It%20is%20the%20prime%20duty%20of%20every%20employer%20to%20provide%20a%20safe%2C%20secure%20and%20positive%20environment%20to%20its%20employees.%20They%20must%20ensure%20that%20everyone%20working%20with%20them%20is%20treated%20with%20dignity%20and%20fairness%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20NHRC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20companies%20create%20better%20workplaces%20where%20employees%20can%20truly%20thrive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20explore%20this%2C%20we%20spoke%20with%20employees%20from%20organisations%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprioritise%20wellbeing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20HR%20experts%20who%20design%20employee-friendly%20policies%2C%20employers%20who%20champion%20flexible%20work%20cultures%2C%20and%20mental%20health%20organisations%20that%20collaborate%20with%20companies%20to%20foster%20overall%20wellness.%20Their%20insights%20provide%20valuable%20answers%20to%20building%20healthier%2C%20more%20supportive%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECompanies%20that%20walk%20the%20talk%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20dedicate%20our%20lives%20to%20work%2C%20often%20without%20realising%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20missing%20out%20on%20precious%20time%20with%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20ourselves.%20Roshne%20Balasubramanian%20%E2%80%94%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20now%20senior%20manager%20of%20communications%20at%20the%20Nalandaway%20Foundation%2C%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20%E2%80%94%20admits%20to%20having%20done%20the%20same%20in%20her%20previous%20roles.%20She%20worked%20in%20toxic%20environments%20that%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20both%20her%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20her%20mother%20fell%20ill%2C%20Roshne%20was%20forced%20to%20reassess%20her%20priorities%2C%20ultimately%20leaving%20journalism.%20She%20describes%20Nalandaway%20a