the%20best%20bet%20to%20free%20them%20from%20the%20labour%20force.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20eight%20residential%20schools%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20curriculum%20focused%20on%20Tamil%20and%20English%20literature%2C%20mathematics%2C%20physical%20education%2C%20and%20activity-based%20learning.%20We%20also%20invested%20in%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20counselling%20and%20would%20track%20their%20progress%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20Nearly%2040%2C000%20children%20benefited%20from%20these%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sankar%20notes.%20But%2C%20she%20says%2C%20they%20deduced%20that%20broader%20social%20sensitisation%20was%20needed%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue%20of%20child%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20in%20time%2C%20the%20vision%20was%20extrapolated%20to%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20families%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F127941%2Fhimachali-health-worker-vaccinate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunity%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20skills%20development%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20job%20creation.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20a%20pan-Indian%20NGO%20rewriting%20the%20story%20of%20rural%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sankar%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Percy%20Barnevik%20(L)%20and%20Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20(R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-d