nt-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20encouraged%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Bibipur%20to%20participate%20in%20village%20decisions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirm%20in%20his%20resolve%20to%20change%20this%20chauvinist%20mentality%2C%20Jaglan%20says%20he%20began%20urging%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Echaupals%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20meetings)%2C%20supported%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20sisters%2C%20and%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202012%2C%20we%20set%20up%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20women%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20ripple%20effect%20this%20had%20was%20tremendous%2C%20and%20Jaglan%20decided%20to%20go%20a%20step%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hosted%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202012%20in%20Bibipur.%20An%20unofficial%20meeting%20of%20clans%20across%20villages%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20historically%20headed%20and%20attended%20by%20men.%20But%20the%20one%20that%20Jaglan%20hosted%20saw%202%2C000%20women%20from%20across%20India%20convene%20to%20discuss%20the%20issues%20that%20oppressed%20their%20female%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20historic%20win!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20issues%20discussed%20were%20domestic%20violence%2C%20%3Cem%3Edowry%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20payment%20given%20to%20the%20groom%20by%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20family%20during%20marriage)%2C%20and%20pressure%20to%20abort%20baby%20girl%20foetuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20of%20the%20Bibipur%20model%20have%20trickled%20into%20Gurugram.%20As%20Ramchander%2C%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20Makhrola%20village%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20of%20village%20development%20was%20introduced%20in%20our%20village%20a%20year%20ago.%20While%20on%20paper%2C%20women%20had%20an%20equal%20participation%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359001%2Fias-officer-balika-panchayat-nanded-maharashtra-young-girls-fight-alcoholism-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epanchayat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecommittees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reality%20was%20very%20different.%20Their%20husbands%20would%20be%20attending%20in%20place%20of%20them.%20But%20now%2C%20women%20are%20not%20only%20called%20for%20assemblies%2C%20they%20actively%20participate%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Jaglan%20spoke%20to%20women%20about%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20female%20foeticide%2C%20dowry%2C%20harassment%20and%20domestic%20violence%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20spoke%20to%20women%20about%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20female%20foeticide%2C%20dowry%2C%20harassment%20and%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDadi%20chahegi%20toh%20poti%20aayegi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20wit