%2Fnovocarry-1726751585.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366790%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKomal%20Panda%20is%20the%20national%20winner%20of%20the%20James%20Dyson%202024%20award%20for%20her%20innovation%20Novocarry.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deeper%20she%20dived%2C%20the%20more%20curious%20she%20became.%20And%20now%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354461%2Fanti-microbial-water-bottles-tanks-mattresses-anasuya-roy-iit-delhi-phd-active-copper-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20innovation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20James%20Dyson-recognised%2C%20she%20is%20elated.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20announced%20the%20national%20award%20winner%2C%20it%20was%20such%20validation.%20It%20assured%20me%20that%20my%20product%20was%20not%20just%20%E2%80%98usable%E2%80%99%20but%20also%20%E2%80%98desirable%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20special%20since%20my%20forte%20isn%E2%80%99t%20in%20engineering.%E2%80%9D%20That%20being%20said%2C%20she%20credits%20the%20faculty%20at%20NID%20who%20chipped%20in%20to%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20prototype%20version%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Komal%20says%20resembled%20a%20bulky%20tiffin%20box%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20final%20version%20developed%20a%20year%20later%2C%20which%20is%20sleekness%20personified%2C%20Novocarry%20has%20had%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20study%2C%20101%20million%20people%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%2011.4%20percent%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%94%20are%20living%20with%20diabetes.%20Novocarry%20could%20provide%20them%20a%20much-needed%20respite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKomal%20explains%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314446%2Fchennai-student-eco-friendly-tech-increases-produce-shelf-life-sunharvested-coolrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20thermoelectric%20cooling%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TEC)%20technology%20is%20the%20work%20of%20the%20Peltier%20chip%20technology.%20The%20heatsinks%2C%20shaped%20like%20bullet%20cartridges%2C%20maintain%20a%20consistent%20temperature%20of%20around%205%20degrees%20Celsius.%20By%20snugly%20wrapping%20around%20the%20vials%2C%20they%20effectively%20cool%20them.%20The%20fans%20force%20air%20into%20the%20device%2C%20bolstering%20the%20cooling%20effect.%20This%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20beer%20and%20vaccine%20coolers%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%2020-inch%20powerhouse%20has%20ample%20storage%20space%20for%20diabetics%20to%20store%20their%20injection%20pens%2C%20needles%2C%20vials%2C%20and%20alcohol%20swabs.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20dual-battery%20system%20eliminates%20any%20frenzy%20over%20low%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_-r4zJO6uk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_-r4zJO6uk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20o